{"article_id":"cnwpQ2Bjb7AK8MRi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President-elect Donald Trump confirmed Thursday","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"that retired Marine Corps Gen. James Mattis will soon be named the new administration ' s pick for Secretary of Defense .","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"\" We ' re not announcing it ' til next week ,","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"so don ' t tell anyone , \"","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"Mr. Trump told a cheering crowd in Cincinnati Thursday evening ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"referring to the nominee by his nickname , \" Mad Dog \"","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"and calling him \" the closest thing","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"we have to George Patton . \"","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"It is what many former military officials consider a \" good news , bad news \" story for the Pentagon ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"which ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"despite its implicit focus on waging war ,","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"has a long","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"- and necessary ,","depth":14},{"id":13,"text":"analysts are quick to add -","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"tradition of civilian , rather than military , leadership .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"\" The good news is that he ' s incredibly competent","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and knows what wars mean , \"","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"says retired Gen. David Barno , a three-star general","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"who commanded US troops in Afghanistan from 2003 to 2005 .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"\" The bad news is that it narrows the field , in my view , of diverse opinions","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"- maybe more than is advisable . \"","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"It is a concern","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that the Trump transition team has acknowledged ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"particularly given that Mattis would be the second retired general","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"tapped","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"to serve in the administration ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"and Trump is said to be eying a third .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"He has named a former three-star general","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"who clashed with the Obama administration ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"Michael Flynn , as his national security advisor .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"The president-elect is also said to be considering for secretary of State retired four-star Gen. David Petraeus ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"who formerly ran both the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan and the CIA","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"-","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"before being forced to resign","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"after being convicted of mishandling classified documents .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"\" It begins to look like Chile in the 1970s , \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"one source","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"advising the Trump team","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"told U.S. News & World Report .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Those sorts of unpleasant optics","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"- of a kind","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that imply military dictatorship , or at least heavy rule -","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"were anticipated by Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"which has a law in place","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"restricting retired military officers from serving as secretary of Defense for a period of seven years","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"after leaving active duty .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Anything less requires a waiver from Congress .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Mattis ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who retired in March 2013 ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"has been out for less than four years .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"There has been one exception","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"made to this law in US history ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"when President Harry Truman appointed former Secretary of State and retired Gen. George Marshall to serve as secretary of Defense in 1950 .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" Congress must not take any changes to this law lightly ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"even if they simply amount to carving out an exception for Gen. Mattis , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"the left-leaning Center for American Progress said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"\" This law exists","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"to preserve civilian control of the military , a cornerstone of American democracy . \"","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"It was a warning","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"echoed this week by lawmakers as well .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Kirsten Gillibrand","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"( D )","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"of New York ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"a member of the Senate Armed Services Committee","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"( SASC ) ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"noted","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"while she \" deeply \" respects Mattis ' s service ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"she will oppose a waiver .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"\" Civilian control is a fundamental principle of American democracy ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"and I will not vote for an exception to this rule , \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"she said in a statement","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"issued Thursday evening .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"The SASC committee chairman , Sen. John McCain","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"( R )","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"of Arizona and a former Vietnam Navy fighter pilot and prisoner of war , was not as concerned .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"\" I look forward to moving forward with the confirmation process as soon as possible in the new Congress , \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"he said in his statement","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"calling Mattis \" without a doubt one of the finest military officers of his generation and an extraordinary leader","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who inspires a rare and special admiration of his troops . \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Mattis ' s salty Marine persona , complete with generous smatterings of profanity , is the stuff of Internet meme legend .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"\" Be polite ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"be professional ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"but have a plan","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"to kill everybody","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"you meet , \"","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"is one of his tamer exhortations from his Iraq command days .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"On fighting the Taliban ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"including \" guys","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"who slap women around for five years","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"because they don ' t wear a veil , \"","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"he said :","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"\" Guys like that ain ' t got no manhood left anyway .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"So it ' s a hell of a lot of fun to shoot them . \"","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Being a successful military officer","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"who rises to the rank of general , particularly in the infantry ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"often requires a decent flair for performance","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"where the troops are concerned .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"In the film \" Patton , \"","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"likely seen by a Trump","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"who has favorably compared him to Mattis ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"the legendary World War II general fires up his soldiers before battle :","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"\" We ' re going to attack all night ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"we ' re gon na attack tomorrow morning , \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"he yells .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"\" If we are not victorious ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"let no man come back alive ! \"","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"When he finishes up his speech ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"one of his colonels implies","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"that he might have been laying it on a bit thick .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"\" You know general ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"sometimes the men don ' t know","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"when you ' re acting , \"","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"he tells Patton .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" It ' s not important for them to know , \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Patton replies , with a wink and a nod .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"\" It ' s only important for me to know . \"","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Mattis , too , relieved an officer","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"for not being aggressive enough in Iraq ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"but he is also considered \" one of the top two or three best-read generals","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"the military has produced in his generation , \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Barno says .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Known for his devotion to the Marine Corps ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Mattis has never married","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"and is known as the \" warrior monk . \"","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"It is this sort of single-minded study of warfare","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"that despite the impression of generals as shoot- ' em-up enthusiasts of bloodshed","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"-which they occasionally enjoy playing into -","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"means that they are also intimately aware of the consequences of war .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"In America ' s current wars , most have spent a decade-and-a-half","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"figuring out how to best spare civilian lives .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"There is the mercenary reason","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"that angry civilians generally do not support the aims of the occupying force ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"but it is also widely believed in an era of modern warfare to be the right thing to do .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Still , Trump clearly treasures the generals for their perceived tough-guy swagger , an image","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"the Queens-raised president-elect likes to cultivate himself .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"But many generals , too , have navigated a highly political military chain of command","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"and make it to the top of their fields","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"because they are savvy and self-aware -","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"and ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"as Patton noted ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"know the difference","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"between playing to the troops","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"they must fire up for war","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"and the sober responsibility for the lives of their soldiers","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"once they actually get into battle .","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"that he was \" surprised , \" for instance ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"that tough-talking Mattis counseled him against the use of torture .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"\" I said ,","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"' What do you think of waterboarding ? ' \"","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Trump told The New York Times .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"\" He","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"[ Mattis ]","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"said ,","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"' I ' ve never found it useful. '","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"He said ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"' I ' ve always found ,","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"give me a pack of cigarettes and a couple of beers","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"and I do better with that","depth":16},{"id":160,"text":"than I do with torture . ' \"","depth":16},{"id":161,"text":"This thorough and often unwelcome knowledge","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"of what can happen to human nature","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"when it meets with the prospect of death and power","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"- and not the movie version of enemies -","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"is why some of the toughest critics of military command are , in fact , the military members themselves .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"\" It is somewhat concerning that Donald Trump continues to eye recently retired generals for some of the most important traditionally civilian positions in government , \"","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"Jon Soltz , an Iraq War veteran and chairman of VoteVets.org , a veterans organization , said in a statement .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"\" While absolutely qualified , and loved by men and women","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"who serve ,","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"we traditionally have had civilian leadership of the Pentagon for a good reason . \" Trump appears to be less concerned with this tradition","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"than he does with the opportunity for good marketing ,","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"Mr. Soltz adds .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"The military is the most respected institution in America ,","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"and Trump loves winners ,","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"as he likes to say .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"\" Trump is selling the brand of generals , \"","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Mr. Soltz says .","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"But the glorification of generals should also give Americans","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"- less than 1 percent of whom have actually served in the military -","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"pause ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"senior military officials have noted with increasing frequency in journal articles and roundtable discussions .","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"\" The founding fathers put democratically elected leaders in control of the military for a reason","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"- so we don ' t end up like a banana republic , \"","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Soltz says .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"although many service members will support Mattis","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"if he receives a congressional waiver ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"as he is expected to ,","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"they remain wary of Trump as a commander-in-chief .","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"In a September poll of military service members","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"conducted by the Military Times and Syracuse University ,","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"68 percent of respondents said","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"they considered Trump ' s temperament \" poor . \"","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"\" He has disrespected women ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"admitted to sexual assault ,","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"trashed the family of a dead trooper ,","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"and trashed Muslims generally ,","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"which undermines any moral authority","depth":17},{"id":199,"text":"we might have in the Middle East , \"","depth":17},{"id":200,"text":"Soltz says .","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"\" There is a concern in the armed forces about this kind of toxic leadership . \"","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"Around the halls of the Pentagon , there also is concern among some services","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"about having both a former Marine","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"serving as Defense Secretary ,","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"and a current Marine","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"serving as chairman of the joint chiefs of staff .","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":208,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":209,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":210,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":211,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":212,"text":"The Marine Corps is the smallest service in the military ,","depth":3},{"id":213,"text":"and its leadership has historically opposed integrating women into combat roles , as well as the repeal of Don ' t Ask , Don ' t Tell , both policies","depth":4},{"id":214,"text":"that came to pass during the Obama administration .","depth":4},{"id":215,"text":"\" Having two","depth":6},{"id":216,"text":"[ of the Pentagon ' s highest leaders ] from that culture is highly unusual","depth":6},{"id":217,"text":"and will potentially impact issues like how women are perceived and what role they get to play inside military services , \"","depth":5},{"id":218,"text":"Barno says .","depth":4},{"id":219,"text":"\" You ' re going to get a pretty strong Marine Corps view of the world . \"","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":439,"left":431,"right":438,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":431,"left":426,"right":430,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":426,"left":313,"right":425,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":272,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":258,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":227,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":221,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":226,"left":223,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":222,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":225,"left":5,"right":224,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":233,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":8,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":9,"right":231,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":230,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":230,"left":10,"right":229,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":229,"left":11,"right":228,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa